two biggest teachers unions weren't swayed by the many educational
overtures and initiatives by Republican George Bush, delegates at
the National Education Association's annual convention vote July 4
on their leaders' recommendation that they support Democrat Al Gore
this fall. We'll try to find out why, and whether the endorsements
do any good. (Mollison, Cox News Service). 22.
