<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-04 21:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2961 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-BIKER-COPS-975(2TAKES     07-04 1012
</HEADER>
